{"tid":1357150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集中討論意見整合po】反恐反三黑清新元朗大行動","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T03:32:04.000Z","uid":263423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6afa316acea313891d7192926f73a9cfdf50fcf6","tid":1357150,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:09:38.000Z","msg":"樓主見好多人話四點大遲<br />\n所以開左po討論元朗<br />\n<br />\n有能力的人請幫忙申請不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">遊行時間：</span><br />\n（前提係共識4點太晏）<br />\n<br />\n請公投<br />\n【公投元朗遊行時間】覺得四點太遲嘅同我入曬嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">散水時間：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&bull;六點</span><br />\n（由元朗人提議，入黑前走）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">遊行標記：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">&bull;</span>申請要寫遊行人士以全護具為記<br />\n》抗議黑警無力保護市民<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">遊行名字：</span><br />\n（暫未有共識）<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">&bull;</span>反恐=令世人知元朗個日係恐襲<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">&bull;</span>反三黑=燒落中共到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">&bull;</span>集合曬-反恐反三黑清新元朗大遊行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">遊行口號：</span><br />\n口號可以拉番政府高官中聯辦為佳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">1.</span>反恐！反黑！反警黑勾結！反政警黑勾結！反共黑勾結！反共恐勾結！反共政警黑勾結！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">2.</span>中聯辦就係新義安，新義安就係中聯辦 <br />\n中聯辦就係和勝和，和勝和就係中聯辦<br />\n中聯辦就係14K，14K就係中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">3.</span>三黑合流 禍港殃民 五大訴求 必須執行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">4</span>.還我安寧元朗 反政警黑合作<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">遊行路線：</span><br />\n由元朗人提供<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">建議一：</span>右面公園，行大馬路到狗屋，上朗屏走<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVVx35z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVVx35z.png&h=26769a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">地圖相關po：</span><br />\n住左廿幾年 精華版元朗地圖 打副本必備<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356339\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356339</a><br />\n<br />\n圍村地圖APP<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354665</a><br />\n<br />\n「長期置頂」727元朗反鄉黑遊行終極攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356464</a>"},{"pid":"1f2fcf8087d362272d03aff7f2a81220b0e6a855","tid":1357150,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:10:09.000Z","msg":"可做行動（集合左其他人意見）：<br />\n1.再重提五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n2.再提宣言（中英都要有）<br />\n<br />\n相關po：<br />\n[置頂][主支線二合一]係元朗讀多次臨時立法會宣言！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1353636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1353636</a><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求去撚咗邊呀屌你（內有721宣言文字版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355616</a><br />\n<br />\n3.提及721連開36槍，追究責任，提有中槍危殆手足（直中頭部）<br />\n<br />\n相關po：<br />\n[721]有手足頭部中槍危殆 吐血不止<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355224</a><br />\n<br />\n［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348209</a><br />\n<br />\n突發（上環有大件發生）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350968</a><br />\n<br />\n4.揭發元朗恐懼為中聯辦黑手，中共政治手段<br />\n［缺決定性證據］<br />\n<br />\n相關po：<br />\n【好緊要！幫推上頂！】美國同阿侵提哂水啦！　香港人下一步係要咁做呀！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354056</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗內幕：「阿爺」下令以暴力懲戒反送中示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355983</a><br />\n<br />\n5.送居民回家行動<br />\n<br />\n6.重申港共為極權政府，人民受極權管治<br />\n以社會信用評級，燈柱入手<br />\n<br />\n7.提出各區成立民間自衛隊<br />\n<br />\n後續：<br />\n1.728死線<br />\n2.728升級？<br />\n<br />\n相關po：<br />\n不如討論下728死線同728行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356131</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ee356f1f511f1100fd1560cea38bb93f74d2e33","tid":1357150,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:11:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查官警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2a4eb5c7aecdc5a063c4142749dcf5e5e5c9ee09","tid":1357150,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:11:45.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n不忘上環手足<br />\n<br />\n大家要關注中槍手足"},{"pid":"9b4d115e1f4626141da52b479cf859127aa8b5d1","tid":1357150,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7jODkt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7jODkt.jpg&h=f23bee54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d460cb65664660bc024410a24df7a1d1688456c","tid":1357150,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:13:45.000Z","msg":"sorry開咁多po！！！"},{"pid":"77e78395e08951792e3692d5be21743e1966bff7","tid":1357150,"uid":167809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"1a97534f6d9728512f384fd72d208dbef36d0515","tid":1357150,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77e78395e08951792e3692d5be21743e1966bff7","tid":1357150,"uid":167809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":